      "blankLabels": ["A", "B", "C", "D"],
      "question": "<div class=\"math-rich-prompt\"><div class=\"math-jp-line\">数列 {a<sub>k</sub>} が</div><div class=\"math-formula\">a<sub>k</sub> = k<sup>2</sup> - 2k + 2　(k ≥ 1)</div><div class=\"math-jp-line\">で与えられているとき，初項から第 n 項までの和は</div><div class=\"math-fraction\"><span class=\"math-frac-top\">A n<sup>3</sup> - B n<sup>2</sup> + C n</span><span class=\"math-frac-bottom\">D</span></div><div class=\"math-jp-line\">である。</div></div>",
      "answer": "1,6,11,6",
      "explanation": {
        "assetType": "text",
        "assetLabel": "老师标准讲解",
        "assetUrl": "demo://eju/math2/sequence/q1/text",
        "summary": "先把和写成 Σ(k^2 - 2k + 2)，再拆成 Σk^2、Σk、Σ1 三部分分别求和，最后整理成分式并读出 A、B、C、D。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "line": "第1步",
            "title": "把总和拆开",
            "detail": "初项到第 n 项的和可写成 Σ(k^2 - 2k + 2) = Σk^2 - 2Σk + 2Σ1。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第2步",
            "title": "套用求和公式",
            "detail": "利用 Σk^2 = n(n+1)(2n+1)/6，Σk = n(n+1)/2，Σ1 = n。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第3步",
            "title": "统一整理",
            "detail": "代入后通分整理，得到 (n^3 - 6n^2 + 11n) / 6，因此 A=1，B=6，C=11，D=6。"
          }
        ],
        "followUp": "如果你对某一步看不懂，可以继续追问“第 2 步为什么可以直接套公式”或“为什么最后要通分”。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "eju-sequence-002",
      "subjectId": "math2",
      "topicId": "sequence",
      "levelId": "basic",
      "abilityIndex": 0,
      "type": "text",
      "blankLabels": ["-AB", "C", "D", "E", "-FGH", "I"],
      "question": "<div class=\"math-rich-prompt\"><div class=\"math-jp-line\">初項 (first term) 2，公比 (common ratio) −<span class=\"math-inline-frac\"><span class=\"math-frac-top\">2</span><span class=\"math-frac-bottom\">3</span></span> の等比数列 (geometric progression) {a<sub>n</sub>} を考える。このとき，b<sub>n</sub> = a<sub>n+1</sub>a<sub>n</sub> (n ≥ 1) とおくと，数列 {b<sub>n</sub>} は</div><div class=\"math-jp-line math-gap-top\">初項 = <span class=\"math-inline-frac\"><span class=\"math-frac-top\">AB</span><span class=\"math-frac-bottom\">C</span></span>，　公比 = <span class=\"math-inline-frac\"><span class=\"math-frac-top\">D</span><span class=\"math-frac-bottom\">E</span></span></div><div class=\"math-jp-line\">の等比数列になる。したがって，</div><div class=\"math-sum-line\"><span class=\"math-sigma\">∑</span><span class=\"math-sum-range\"><span>∞</span><span>n=1</span></span> b<sub>n</sub> = <span class=\"math-inline-frac\"><span class=\"math-frac-top\">FGH</span><span class=\"math-frac-bottom\">I</span></span></div><div class=\"math-jp-line\">である。</div></div>",
      "answer": "-8,3,4,9,-24,5",
      "explanation": {
        "assetType": "text",
        "assetLabel": "老师标准讲解",
        "assetUrl": "demo://eju/math2/sequence/q2/text",
        "summary": "先写出 a_n 的一般项，再利用 b_n = a_{n+1}a_n 求出新等比数列的初项与公比，最后用无穷等比级数求和公式。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "line": "第1步",
            "title": "写出 a_n 的一般项",
            "detail": "由初項 2、公比 −2/3，可得 a_n = 2(−2/3)^{n−1}。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第2步",
            "title": "求 b_n 的初项和公比",
            "detail": "b_n = a_{n+1}a_n = 2(−2/3)^n · 2(−2/3)^{n−1} = −8/3 · (4/9)^{n−1}，所以初项为 −8/3，公比为 4/9。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第3步",
            "title": "求无穷和",
            "detail": "因为 |4/9| < 1，故 ∑_{n=1}^{∞} b_n = (−8/3) / (1 − 4/9) = −24/5。"
          }
        ],
        "followUp": "如果你不明白为什么 b_n 仍然是等比数列，可以继续追问“第 2 步里指数是怎么合并的”。"
      }
    }
  ]
